headline: ResMed (NYSE:RMD) Reports Strong Q3 Earnings Growth and Declares US$0.53 Dividend
summary: Recently, ResMed (NYSE:RMD) reported solid financial performance for the quarter ending March 31, 2025, with sales increasing to $1,292 million and net income reaching $365 million year-over-year. The company declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.53 per share.
